<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>{{ doc.numero }} · Manifiesto de Carga</title>
<style>
  {{ fontStyle | raw }}
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  html, body { margin: 0; }
  :root { --ink: #161411; --ink-2: #57524b; --ink-3: #8c857c; --paper: #fbfaf6; --rule: #161411; --line: #e6e2d9; --accent: #2f5a4a; }
  body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 10px; line-height: 1.45; color: var(--ink); background: var(--paper); width: 794px; min-height: 1123px; padding: 34px 40px; }
  .mono { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
  p { margin: 0; }

  .hero { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto; align-items: end; padding-bottom: 14px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .hero .co .co-name { font-family: 'Newsreader', serif; font-size: 19px; font-weight: 500; }
  .hero .co .co-sub { font-size: 9px; color: var(--ink-2); margin-top: 2px; max-width: 320px; }
  .hero .mid { text-align: right; }
  .hero .mid .doc-kind { font-family: 'Newsreader', serif; font-style: italic; font-size: 16px; }
  .hero .mid .doc-sub { font-size: 8px; color: var(--ink-3); letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-top: 2px; }
  .hero .mid .doc-num { margin-top: 3px; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 500; white-space: nowrap; }

  .factline { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 14px; padding-bottom: 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .factline .k { font-size: 8.5px; color: var(--ink-3); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; }
  .factline .v { font-family: 'Newsreader', serif; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; margin-top: 2px; }

  .section-title { font-family: 'Newsreader', serif; font-style: italic; font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink-2); margin-bottom: 10px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline; }
  .section-title .c { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-size: 8.5px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: var(--ink-3); }

  .items { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; table-layout: fixed; }
  .items thead th { font-size: 8px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.04em; color: var(--ink-3); font-weight: 500; text-align: left; padding: 8px 8px 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); }
  .items tbody td { padding: 9px 8px 9px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); vertical-align: top; font-size: 9px; }
  .items .c-fecha { width: 54px; white-space: nowrap; }
  .items .c-guia { width: 84px; }
  .items .c-placa { width: 52px; white-space: nowrap; }
  .items .c-bul, .items .c-weight, .items .c-flete { text-align: right; }
  .items .c-bul { width: 36px; }
  .items .c-weight { width: 56px; color: var(--ink-2); }
  .items .c-flete { width: 60px; }
  .items .c-pago { width: 74px; padding-right: 0; }
  .items .guia .l { display: flex; gap: 4px; align-items: baseline; }
  .items .guia .tag { font-size: 7px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink-3); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.02em; width: 22px; flex: none; }
  .items .guia .num { font-weight: 500; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 8.5px; white-space: nowrap; }
  .items .party { font-family: 'Newsreader', serif; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; word-break: break-word; }
  .items .pago .t { font-size: 8px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.03em; white-space: nowrap; }
  .items .pago .t.cancelado { color: var(--accent); }
  .items .pago .t.cobrar, .items .pago .t.pce { color: var(--ink-3); }
  .items tfoot td { padding: 11px 8px 0 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--rule); font-weight: 600; font-size: 10px; }
  .items tfoot .lbl { font-family: 'Newsreader', serif; font-style: italic; font-weight: 500; font-size: 12px; }
  .items tfoot .c-bul, .items tfoot .c-weight, .items tfoot .c-flete { text-align: right; }
  .items tfoot .c-flete { padding-left: 6px; }
  .items tfoot .c-pago { padding-right: 0; }

  .foot { margin-top: 22px; padding-top: 14px; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .foot .note { font-size: 9px; color: var(--ink-2); }
  .foot .note strong { color: var(--ink); }
  .foot .note .badge { display: inline-block; color: var(--accent); padding: 3px 0; font-family: 'Newsreader', serif; font-style: italic; font-size: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--accent); margin-bottom: 7px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="co">
    <div class="co-name">{{ doc.emisorRazonSocial }}</div>
    <div class="co-sub">{% if doc.emisorDireccion is not empty %}{{ doc.emisorDireccion }} · {% endif %}RUC {{ doc.emisorRuc }}{% if doc.emisorRegistroMtc is not empty %} · Reg. MTC {{ doc.emisorRegistroMtc }}{% endif %}</div>
  </div>
  <div class="mid">
    <div class="doc-kind">Manifiesto de Carga</div>
    <div class="doc-sub">Documento interno</div>
    <div class="doc-num">{{ doc.numero }}</div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="factline">
  <div><div class="k">Fecha de salida</div><div class="v">{% if doc.fechaSalida is not null %}{{ doc.fechaSalida|date('d/m/Y') }}{% endif %}</div></div>
  <div><div class="k">Serie · N°</div><div class="v">{% if doc.serie is not empty %}{{ doc.serie }} · {% endif %}{{ doc.numero }}</div></div>
  <div><div class="k">Guías · bultos</div><div class="v">{{ doc.totalGuias }} · {{ doc.totalBultos }}</div></div>
  <div><div class="k">Peso · flete</div><div class="v">{{ doc.totalPeso|n_format }} kg · S/ {{ doc.totalFlete|n_format }}</div></div>
</div>

<div class="section-title"><span>Carga consolidada — guías de remisión</span><span class="c">{{ doc.totalGuias }} guías</span></div>
<table class="items">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th class="c-fecha">F. Emisión</th>
      <th class="c-guia">Guía</th>
      <th>Remitente</th>
      <th>Destinatario</th>
      <th class="c-placa">Placa</th>
      <th class="c-bul">Bultos</th>
      <th class="c-weight">Peso kg</th>
      <th class="c-flete">Flete S/</th>
      <th class="c-pago">Pago</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    {% for l in doc.lineas %}
    <tr>
      <td class="c-fecha mono">{% if l.fechaEmision is not null %}{{ l.fechaEmision|date('d/m/Y') }}{% endif %}</td>
      <td class="guia"><div class="l"><span class="tag">Guía</span><span class="num">{{ l.guiaSerieNumero }}</span></div>{% if l.taquito is not empty %}<div class="l"><span class="tag">Taq.</span><span class="num">{{ l.taquito }}</span></div>{% endif %}</td>
      <td class="party">{{ l.remitente }}</td>
      <td class="party">{{ l.destinatario }}</td>
      <td class="c-placa mono">{{ l.placa }}</td>
      <td class="c-bul mono">{{ l.bultos }}</td>
      <td class="c-weight mono">{{ l.peso|n_format }}</td>
      <td class="c-flete mono">{{ l.flete|n_format }}</td>
      <td class="pago">{% if l.condicionPago is not empty %}<span class="t {{ l.pagoClase }}">{{ l.condicionPago }}</span>{% endif %}</td>
    </tr>
    {% endfor %}
  </tbody>
  <tfoot>
    <tr>
      <td class="lbl" colspan="5">Total · {{ doc.totalGuias }} guías consolidadas</td>
      <td class="c-bul mono">{{ doc.totalBultos }}</td>
      <td class="c-weight mono">{{ doc.totalPeso|n_format }}</td>
      <td class="c-flete mono">{{ doc.totalFlete|n_format }}</td>
      <td class="c-pago"></td>
    </tr>
  </tfoot>
</table>

<div class="foot">
  <div class="note">
    <span class="badge">Uso interno</span>
    <p>Documento de <strong>control de carga consolidada</strong> para el viaje. No constituye comprobante de pago ni guía de remisión electrónica; cada guía se sustenta de forma individual.</p>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
